  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/0ede950326c0c3814bfea6b4a0b33fca.poster.avif?t=1663933211\" width=616 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/0ede950326c0c3814bfea6b4a0b33fca.webm?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/0ede950326c0c3814bfea6b4a0b33fca.mp4?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In modern society, the stress that plagues many people ...<br>It has piled up and has reached the limit of this star! !<br><br>Yeah ... it's time to explode the massive amount of stress that has accumulated in you! !<br><br>The cause of stress that hides in everyday life,<br>By destroying, messing up and exploding,<br>Save this world from stress! !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/21cec3aeddc2de412fc2dbf0b31d9e3f.poster.avif?t=1663933211\" width=616 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/21cec3aeddc2de412fc2dbf0b31d9e3f.webm?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/21cec3aeddc2de412fc2dbf0b31d9e3f.mp4?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>This is a 2D action game with a refreshing feeling of destruction in various everyday situations.<br>The purpose of the game is to destroy the bosses prepared for all stages while collecting \"love fragments\" and \"money\" while aiming for a high score in each stage.<br>The protagonist is a person who is trapped in modern stress and fights against various stresses such as daily life, time, company, boss, and noise.<br>The game world is represented by a funny, cute, hand-drawn dot picture.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/7f7baaef4f97c01d02aa31b9a87b23b3.poster.avif?t=1663933211\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/7f7baaef4f97c01d02aa31b9a87b23b3.webm?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/7f7baaef4f97c01d02aa31b9a87b23b3.mp4?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> * Operate the hero to destroy everything.<br><br> * When you destroy something, hero's voltage rises and stress is released.<br><br> * Destroy the boss, which is the source of stress, and clear the stage.<br><br> * The situations and places that the hero faces will be unlocked.<br><br> * Each stage, get a high score, collect \"fragments of love\" and \"money\".<br><br> * Achieve the \"challenge\" prepared for each stage and collect \"happy clovers\".<br><br> * Build trees, stones, and buildings on the MAP to raise the hero's status.<br><br> * Anyway, let's blow everything up with stress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/c23c43034b930e68fdbc35338bb7af1d.poster.avif?t=1663933211\" width=78 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/c23c43034b930e68fdbc35338bb7af1d.webm?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>When you've blown out all the stress...<br>May peace come to the world and you.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/0ede950326c0c3814bfea6b4a0b33fca.poster.avif?t=1663933211\" width=616 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/0ede950326c0c3814bfea6b4a0b33fca.webm?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/0ede950326c0c3814bfea6b4a0b33fca.mp4?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In modern society, the stress that plagues many people ...<br>It has piled up and has reached the limit of this star! !<br><br>Yeah ... it's time to explode the massive amount of stress that has accumulated in you! !<br><br>The cause of stress that hides in everyday life,<br>By destroying, messing up and exploding,<br>Save this world from stress! !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/21cec3aeddc2de412fc2dbf0b31d9e3f.poster.avif?t=1663933211\" width=616 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/21cec3aeddc2de412fc2dbf0b31d9e3f.webm?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/21cec3aeddc2de412fc2dbf0b31d9e3f.mp4?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>This is a 2D action game with a refreshing feeling of destruction in various everyday situations.<br>The purpose of the game is to destroy the bosses prepared for all stages while collecting \"love fragments\" and \"money\" while aiming for a high score in each stage.<br>The protagonist is a person who is trapped in modern stress and fights against various stresses such as daily life, time, company, boss, and noise.<br>The game world is represented by a funny, cute, hand-drawn dot picture.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/7f7baaef4f97c01d02aa31b9a87b23b3.poster.avif?t=1663933211\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/7f7baaef4f97c01d02aa31b9a87b23b3.webm?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/7f7baaef4f97c01d02aa31b9a87b23b3.mp4?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> * Operate the hero to destroy everything.<br><br> * When you destroy something, hero's voltage rises and stress is released.<br><br> * Destroy the boss, which is the source of stress, and clear the stage.<br><br> * The situations and places that the hero faces will be unlocked.<br><br> * Each stage, get a high score, collect \"fragments of love\" and \"money\".<br><br> * Achieve the \"challenge\" prepared for each stage and collect \"happy clovers\".<br><br> * Build trees, stones, and buildings on the MAP to raise the hero's status.<br><br> * Anyway, let's blow everything up with stress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/c23c43034b930e68fdbc35338bb7af1d.poster.avif?t=1663933211\" width=78 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1291640/extras/c23c43034b930e68fdbc35338bb7af1d.webm?t=1663933211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>When you've blown out all the stress...<br>May peace come to the world and you.",
